WELCOME 안녕하세요

I am only able to play at Internet-Café at the moment!



Banner made by Mastra1234 - Thank you!


Banner made by Donger Deluxe


Thank you Mastra1234 for the banner and the profile picture!


My Internet sucks. I have to play in Internet Café to play online...

I don't look at the osu!chat, so don't be angry, if I don't answer .-.

NEW PLAYSTYLE


Started with KSM again


MY YOUTUBE (looks like crap atm): https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpeIm2 ... FHdgE-vVuA





Important (I think)
Please don't be angry, if I don't answer in-game.
I'm not looking at the chat that much

I'm looking for a new cam for my videos. If you can recommend me one, please send me pm



Skins and Playstyle
Skins:
4k-5k > Staiain's skin/ Stepmania skin
6-8k > sometimes Staiain's skin but mostly O2JAM or Beatmania skin

Playstyle:
4k: [n] [m] [1] [2] - Sometimes [x] [c] [m] [,]
5k: [x] [c] (space) [m] [,]
6k: [z] [x] [c] [M] [,] [.]
7k: [z] [x] [c] (space) [m] [,] [.]
8k: [\] [z] [x] [c] (space) [m] [,] [.]
